<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بينهما عشرة أميال.<span class="c5"> يعني:</span> بين <span class="c2">(مكة)</span> و <span class="c2">(سرِف)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
